overview.en: Moses is a based on Ethernet fang male chain development platform for the decentralized prediction, Moses by block chain of public environment and cryptography, asymmetric encryption algorithm, the combination of intelligent contract, to provide users with different types of prediction, besides platform provides predict events, users can also create forecast events, participate in predicting outcome events and correct the user will be rewarded, and the wisdom of the masses into full play
overview.zh: Moses 是一款基于以太坊公链开发的去中心化预测平台，Moses通过区块链的公开环境以及与密码学、 非对称加密算法、智能合约的结合，为用户提供不同类型的预测事件，除了平台提供的预测事件外，用户还可以自主创建预测事件，参与预测事件结果并正确的用户将获得奖励，从而发挥大众的智慧
